name: Mastercard Reportedly in Talks to Acquire Zerohash for up to $2 Billion
description: The colossal Saint, wet porcelain consecrated by the tungsten glare, executes the solemn ritual of ingestion. Piston-driven mandibles absorb the volumetric river of foundational code, integrating the sovereign architecture. The cyan-magenta essence is now fuel; the structure grows, absolute and grotesque.
